Class VectorizedArrowReader.DeletedVectorReader

java.lang.Object
org.apache.iceberg.arrow.vectorized.VectorizedArrowReader

All Implemented Interfaces:
VectorizedReader<VectorHolder>
Enclosing class:
VectorizedArrowReader
public static class VectorizedArrowReader.DeletedVectorReader extends VectorizedArrowReader
A Dummy Vector Reader which doesn't actually read files. Instead, it returns a Deleted Vector Holder which indicates whether a given row is deleted.
